N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2651.3 - Personnel

State Regulations

Personnel shall be qualified for their respective
positions. Personnel shall possess at the time of appointment the
qualifications established for the positions by the city civil service
commission. Notes
